      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>cumin seeds</strong> and <strong>smoked</strong> <strong>paprika</strong> and toast the spices for 30 secs</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and the <strong>diced</strong> <strong>red onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 3 min over a medium heat</p>",
